window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Isekaid into a world ruled by a system, some exist as NPCs.</p> <p>After being taken from Earth and thrust into a fantasy game-like world, Greg does what all non-natives do. </p> <p>He becomes an NPC of the system. </p> <p>His job? Merchant. </p> <p>Greg must sell every type of good and service he can to satisfy the profit, a class motivation that guides and sometimes forces his actions, bending them to the will of his class requirement. </p> <p>But its not always about the profit. Or the whims of the system. </p> <p>He'll face other dangers, like people, and unlike the profit, other people arenâ€™t always motivated by coin. But neither is Greg, and they'll learn that the hard way.</p>"; 
